    "8e9a1708-04be-4188-9dc0-5192d83cbe3f": {
      "type": "media-with-tabs",
      "blocks": {
        "8c72fabf-0c28-4510-8941-2315b4385141": {
          "type": "loop_video",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Preview",
            "text": "<p>DZHUS ethical transformer clothing brand and White Mandarin natural selfcare label present “Kinship” visual project celebrating a unique synthesis of various designer objects, united by eco-inspired, surrealistic aesthetics.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "target_blank": false,
            "button_style": "outlined"
          }
        },
        "template--18483371475218__8e9a1708-04be-4188-9dc0-5192d83cbe3f-16819804643ac36f87-1": {
          "type": "video",
          "settings": {
            "video_load": "https://youtu.be/LSLn4VV335g",
            "video_alt": "",
            "heading": "Watch promo",
            "text": "<p>The art director of the collab, Irina Dzhus, has gathered multipurpose garments, interior decor, authentic ceramics, 3D-printed jewellery, cruelty-free shoes, and avant-garde pastry in one space. The unusual beauty looks were created using natural skincare and haircare products.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "target_blank": false,
            "button_style": "outlined"
          }
        },
        "template--18483371475218__8e9a1708-04be-4188-9dc0-5192d83cbe3f-16819804643ac36f87-0": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Biomorphic shapes",
            "text": "<p>The series of abstract compositions highlighting domestic scenes is implemented in white monochrome, whereas all the details speculate on corporeality and biomorphic shapes.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "target_blank": false,
            "button_style": "outlined"
          }
        },
        "d6e4d396-0696-4102-802e-029535f33c0f": {
          "type": "image",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "conscious happiness",
            "text": "<p>The project’s ideologists, DZHUS and White Mandarin, have consolidated their creative forces to honour a complex approach to formation of a harmonious and self-sufficient personality, and to glorify synergetic elements of conscious happiness.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "target_blank": false,
            "button_style": "outlined"
          }
        },
        "5c3cdd18-2021-47cc-abb5-f945258ad282": {
          "type": "image",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Contributors",
            "text": "<p>Ethical transformer clothing: @dzhus.conceptual.wear | Natural selfcare products: @market.choice.ua | Interior objects: @fainadesign | Location: @ya.vsesvit @yakusha.design | Art confectionery: @sugarylab_cakestudio | Cruelty-free footwear: @housemartin_footwear | 3D-printed jewellery: @ladalegina | Art direction, styling, casting: @irina.dzhus | Photo: @pnmrvalexey | Video: @_sergey_vovk_ | Makeup: @mua_model | Hair: @julia_danshyna   | Models: @lenka_klymenko / @sofipashkual, @wasssabidi | Styling assistants: @anatoliielgert, @darynatrukhachova, @nat_kohler_</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "target_blank": false,
            "button_style": "outlined"
          }
        }
      },
